Django Web-Development:

install python-setuptools
install easy_install virtualenv==1.10.1
	{
		Setup virtual Environment cmd:virtualenv --no-site-packages 'django'(this is the foldername)
	}
To activate Virtual Enviroment type cmd:source django/bin/activate
To deactive type:deactivate

Then go inside the newly Created Folder and install Django:easy_install Django

To create project cmd:django-admin.py startproject "ProjectName"

To Run web-server cmd:python manage.py runserver (localhost)

